stream
BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 158.88 610 Td (YOU ARE NOT ALONE) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 40 600 m 392 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 575 Td (Dear Mama \(or Papa\),) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 561 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 547 Td (I am so deeply sorry for your loss. The baby you carried, no matter) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 533 Td (how briefly, was real. Your love was real. Your grief is real.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 519 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 505 Td (You may have heard:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 491 Td ('At least you know you can get pregnant.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 477 Td ('It was not meant to be.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 463 Td ('You can always try again.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 449 Td ('At least it was early.') Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 435 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 421 Td (None of those words help. None of them honor what you lost.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 407 Td (What you lost was a PERSON. A future. A hope. A part of yourself.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 393 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 379 Td (This journal is your safe space. There are no right or wrong) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 365 Td (answers. There is no timeline for grief. There is no 'getting over) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 351 Td (it' - there is only learning to carry it.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 337 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 323 Td (You may use this journal every day, or you may pick it up only) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 309 Td (when the waves of grief feel too heavy to carry alone.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 295 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 281 Td (Your baby existed. Your baby mattered. Your baby is still loved.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 267 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 253 Td (With compassion and understanding,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9 Tf 40 239 Td (Daniel Tesfamariam) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
